'''The Tolkien Calendar 1993''' was published in Poland by Sekji Tolkienowskiej. This calendar features pen and ink illustrations by [[Aleksandra Kosciuszczuk]], [[Ryszard Derdziński]], [[Małgorzata Pudlik]], and [[Helena Strokowska]].

* Dimensions: 8 1/4 x 11 5/8 inches
* Not stapled
